IMAPAccount main
Host $email_imap_hostname
User $email_username
Pass $email_password
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore main-remote
Account main

MaildirStore main-local
Path $email_maildir_path/
Inbox $email_maildir_path/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel main
Master :main-remote:
Slave :main-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
